description:
Broadcast on KPFA, Feb. 23, 1983 | On Israel's military industry and its role in Central America. Statements by Arnaldo Ramos, Arnon Hadar, Marc Allen, Francisco Garrett, Mark VanderHoud, Jane Rassmussen, and Louis Wolf.
